---
title: Double Char Siu Beef Noodle Stir-Fry with Mixed Veggies & Spring Onion
description: Fire up your taste buds with this sweet and savoury stir-fry! Beef mince is flavoured with sweet soy seasoning, and tossed
together with tender veggies and golden egg noodles in a char siu sauce. You’ll be slurping up every last bit.
